      <h1 class="content-hero-title">Ibogaine</h1>
      <p class="content-hero-subtitle">Ibogaine is one of the most pharmacologically complex and clinically significant psychoactive compounds known. Its extraordinary promise in treating opioid dependence exists alongside one of the most serious safety profiles in psychedelic medicine. Understanding both &mdash; in full &mdash; is essential before engaging with it.</p>
